Title: Fire in the Hole
Plot: When a mole in the treasury department is discovered and the framed suspect in the Armenian money train robbery turns up missing, the Strike team race to find the suspect before their cover is blown.  Meanwhile, Claudette attempts to make amends with the Decoy Squad by going undercover to help them on a case.
GuestStars: Natalie Zea, David Rees Snell, Cathy Cahlin Ryan, Brian J. White, RonReaco Lee, Mo, Michael Phenicie, Nicki Micheaux, Gareth Williams, Andrew Borba
